text:
Very nice place with a calm and quite atmosphere. Good place to take family and to go with friends for some good conversation. They are serving really awsome food with very quick pace. 
But, if you are taking more than 10 people at a time , it will be difficult to find a place to accommodate everyone around the same table. 
They do not have a dedicated parking space. But you can avail the pay and park option available very next to this place 
Porotta and beef fry is my fav food here ☺️
Chicken noodles was great & also the quantity of tea/coffee served was above normal which is generally served at other places

Good food, the restaurant has both AC and outdoor dining. The road is usually busy and you might not found parking close to the restaurant free. The sevice is good and worth visiting with your family for a dinner night.
Nice place to gather with family and friends. Well arranged seating. Tasty indian, chinese, arabian dishes. Affordable price.
Good place for a hangout wit friends & family... It has a nice atmosphere... It's clean n sparkly... Loved the food too... I always order food from there in swiggy. My fav is the triple fried rice...
